  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed erection of a second floor rear extension by reason of excessive scale, bulk and massing is considered to be an overdominant form of development which would bear no relationship to the existing scale and context of the host building and existing terrace. It would also have a detrimental impact on the character and appearance of the conservation area and the amenities of the adjoining residents contrary to policies D3 (Site Planning), D4 (Designing in context), D11 (Alterations and extensions) and D28 (Rear Extensions) of Islington's Unitary Development Plan 2002, Islington's Urban Design guidance 2006 and the National Planning Policy Framework 2012."
